sub_title: Equity Analyst in Thematic Investing at Robeco | Ex-Consultant @KPMG | Economics @Bocconi University | Quantitative Analysis & Research
summary:
I am a curious, open-minded young professional, eager to learn and challenge myself. My background in economics helps me to always watch the broader picture and to rigorously analyse data and facts to support opinions. I am open to diverse and engaging experiences in the world of consultancy, business and finance, especially if related to my interests for innovation and technology, or for the macroeconomics mechanisms working behind our economy.

A routine without a routine. No typical day. The experience of a huge variety of activities, as well as the opportunity to challenge myself and all my diverse skills. Explore my personality from every angle. Explore each one of my potential strengths. This really is what I want my career being based on. 

Satisfaction. Improvement. Challenges. Opportunities to grow. 
These will be the building blocks.
